sentence.text: My oldest pet is a mongrel dog |T| called Mickey .
Mickey ’s body is black but he has a white stomach , white feet , a white streak down his nose , and a white fluffet on the end of his tail .
He was bought when he was only a puppy of three weeks at Christmas ; that was almost seven years ago .
Being blind at_first Mickey always kept bumping into objects that were in his path but as his eyes formed he began to see .
# What I thought was a most humorous action by Mickey was # when he discovered the staircase .
Mickey clambered up in his puppy ways and when arriving on the top step he realised the height and his terror would not let him down .
He immediately whimpered continually until someone came up the stairs and ‘ rescued ’ him .
Nowadays he is an extremely intelligent dog .
My father is on shift work and Mickey can tell which shift he is on .
When # on night shift my father comes home in the morning and under all circumstances Mickey will welcome him .
He listens for the car door and then waits for dad .
